Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,《德古拉》前情回顾\NPreviously on Dracula...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Daniel！\NDaniel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,…Alecander Grayson…我的一切…\N...Alecander Grayson...the whole of my world...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson\NGrayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我为各位展现  无线能源\NI give to you wireless power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,实验出现了一些技术难题  先生\NExperiencing some technical difficulties, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我发誓…  - 我们见过？\N- I'd swear. - We've met?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我也这样想\NYes, I was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底需要在黑暗中呆多久？\NHow long must I spend skulking in the shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想如常人一样在阳光下行走\NI wanna walk in the sun like any other man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  太阳\NSir, the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼\NDamn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你做我丈夫  我嫁你为妻\NBe my husband, and I will be your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在想什么？  - 想你\N- What are you thinking about?  - You.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.67,0:00:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想Jayne女士\NI was thinking about Lady Jayne
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  还有她那猎杀行动\NWetherby and her vampire hunting, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在先知死了\NNow that the seers are dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那他召唤他的族类\Nhe will much more easily
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就更轻而易举了\Nattract others of his kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不久  伦敦就会斥满祸害\NSoon, London will be crawling with the vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jayne女士是个猎人\NLady Jayne is a huntsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看来恶龙会\NSeems the Ordo Draco is more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,比我们预期的更有先见之明\Nforward-thinking than I gave it credit for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,诡异时光啊\NStrange times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,相当诡异\NWonderfully strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你得杀了她  - 如果我杀了她\N- You'll kill her. - If I kill her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会只会找其他人取而代之\Nthe Order will just send somebody else to replace her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要断了你俩的联系\NYou'll end it with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要这样做？\NNow why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她是吸血鬼猎人\NShe's a vampire hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield  我要做的不仅是\NRenfield, not only will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,消除她仅有的怀疑\NI evade her slightest suspicion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还要拿走她从未给过别人的东西\NI'll take from her a prize she's given no other man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她的爱  - 不是\N- Her love. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,比这更珍贵的…\NSomething far more precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她的信任\NHer trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,订两个明晚的位子\NMake a reservation tomorrow night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,八点  Savoy酒店\N8：00, for two at the Savoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  要主厅里最显眼的位子\NThe most exclusive, visible table in the main dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  主人\NHello, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,根据腐烂情况来看\NGiven the extent of the putrefaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女性最年轻\NI say the female is the youngest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,被转五年  甚至更少\Nfive years sired, maybe less.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而另一方面  这一个\NThis one, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,明显老得多\Nis clearly much older,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,最少活了一世纪\Na century undead at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说  这两个吸血鬼\NI mean, that said, neither of the vampires
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,都不足以杀死先知\Nare old enough to be the ones that killed our seers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那逃掉的那个呢？\NBut the one who eluded you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是他们的创造者\NThere, sire, I suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,比他们更年长\Nwhich would make him older still.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们在寻找的吗？\NOld enough to be the one we're searching for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  他将是一个劲敌\NOh, he will be a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 劲敌？  - Browning先生  如果是\N- formidable? - If so, Mr. Browning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就只有上帝能帮助你了\Nthen God help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果连我都杀不了他\Nbecause if I can't kill the beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就没人可以了\Nno one can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Josef Cervenka啊\NJosef Cervenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的得力右臂\NMy right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都过去很久了\NA long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,胡说\NNonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你将再一次成为我手下战将\NYou are once more under my battlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,召唤你来是有原因的  很快\NI summoned you here for a reason, and very soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们就会摧毁我们的宿敌  - 恶龙会？\N- we shall destroy our greatest enemy. - The Ordo Draco?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NThe same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经发现新的技术\NRich men who've bet their future on oil,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来摧毁\Nbut I've discovered a technology
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对石油孤注一掷的大亨们\Nthat will destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但他们比以前更强大  - 说确切点\N- But they are stronger than ever. Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就在今晚\NJust this night,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我目睹我的两个幼类被猎人屠杀\NI saw two of my brood slaughtered by a huntsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还是个女的\Na female of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我需要你的帮助\NThat's why I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识她\NI know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就把她抽筋削骨了\NThen we will peel the flesh from her bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还不到时候\NNot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下饺子式的杀害不能将他们击败\NWe cannot defeat them by killing them one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得直捣他们的权利之源\NWe must attack the source of their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的财富\NTheir wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,像寻常小偷那样偷走他们的钱包？\NTo pick their pockets like a common thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那样毫无尊严\NThere's no honor in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  先生  我听到动静\NI'm sorry, sir. I heard voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield  见见我的…\NRenfield, this is my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,老朋友  Josef Cervenka\Nold friend Josef Cervenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他想住这里多久\NHe will be staying in this house
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就住多久\Nas long as he wishes.
