Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB72BD1&\fn华文行楷\fs28\pos(370,309)}—— 德 古 拉 ——\N第一季 第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人吃惊\NSuch a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候  Daniel就被诊断出心律紊乱\NAs a boy, Daniel was diagnosed with an irregular heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我想发作  也只是时间问题罢了\NI supposed it was just a matter of time before it gave out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  这个年纪就死于心脏病\NStill, he was so young
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他还是太年轻了\Nto die of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我应该感谢上帝\NMaybe I should just thank
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们曾经相处那么久\Nthe lord for the time we did have together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要用牡丹和苹果花花环\NWe shall drape the walls and the ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,装扮墙壁和天花板\Nwith garlands of peonies and apple blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你一下如何  Harker？\NWhat do you think, Harker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  只要Mina喜欢就好\NOh, whatever pleases Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我想给她一个完美的订婚宴\NI want this engagement party to be perfect for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  Grayson先生  你确定…\NThank you, Mr. Grayson. Are you quite sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我很荣幸来主办你们的订婚宴\NIt'll be honor to host your engagement party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还有大烛台\NAnd candelabras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,随处可见的银质大烛台\NSilver candelabras everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,置于桌上\Non the tables
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,点缀花饰\Nand in all the floral arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,会有大烛台的\NCandelabras it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina？Mina  亲爱的  过来\NMina? Mina, darling, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你怎样出场\NI want to show you how you're going to make your entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,马上回来\NOne moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\NI want you to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎样看Arthur Ogilvy将军的\Nwhat you think about General Arthur Ogilvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像积极的\NIt seems he's the military's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,支持对奥斯曼帝国开战\Nleading advocate for war against the Ottoman Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只是表面现象而已  - 怎么说\N- Well, appearances can be deceiving. - Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,私下里  他反对战争\NIn private, he opposes the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的好战分子是副将\NThe real advocate is his number two,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Colin Shaw将军  战争英雄\NGeneral Colin Shaw, the war hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,深受公众拥护\NVery popular in the public sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,额  这位战争英雄\NHmm, and yet this war hero
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为了控制区域里的石油储备\Nis willing to spill
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,竟不惜血流成河\Nan ocean of blood to control the region's vast oil reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但Shaw将军坚信奥斯曼是个威胁\NBut General Shaw believes the Ottomans are a real threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会以为\NYou're not suggesting he's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他是为了个人利益而发动战争吧\Nadvocating war for personal financial gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个傀儡\NHe's a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,掌权者将身家性命\NPowerful men have staked their fortunes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都压在了被视为未来燃料的石油上\Non the presumption that the future will be fueled by oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看来他们不仅是对奥斯曼帝国宣战了\NIt seems they've not only declared
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还想对Grayson能源下手\Nwar on the Ottoman Empire, but on Grayson energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我\NYou and me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,以及我们努力打拼的一切\Nand everything we worked so hard for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抬头  Lucy\NHead up, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能只是走下楼梯  像滑的\NYou don't walk down the stairs, you glide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你尽力查出\NI want you to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个Shaw将军的一切  Harker\Neverything you can about this General Shaw, Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他的癖好   他的软弱\NHis weaknesses. His failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  除非  你还想\NUnless, of course, you'd like
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,呆在这儿  讨论鲜花布置\Nto stay here and discuss floral arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我办吧\NLeave it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina\NMina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你得从这儿入场\NMake your entrance from down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,烟花  餐前酒必须搭配烟花啊\NFireworks, we must have fireworks with our aperitifs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy  别说了\NLucy, do stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你会让Grayson先生后悔出此好意的\NYou'll make Mr. Grayson regret his hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 胡说  - 准备好下一轮测试了\N- Nonsense.- We're ready for another test run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们  这是我的首席工程师\NLadies, this is my chief engineer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kowalski先生\NMr. Kowalski.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我等会儿就下去\NI'll be down in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他是在说共振机吗？\NIs he referring to the resonator machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你在测试吗？ 只是些日常工作\N- Are you testing it now? - Just routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要留下观看的话  没问题\NIf you'd like to stay and watch, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 主啊 Mina 我们一定要看吗？\N Oh, lord, Mina, must we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Westernra小姐\NMiss Westenra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要离开  我可以帮你安排\NIf you wish to leave, I can easily arrange
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,给Murray小姐再加一辆马车\Na second carriage for Miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请和以往一样尽情享受\NEnjoy, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为所有事情都井然有条 Kowalski先生\NI presume everything is in order, Mr. Kowalski.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,开始第一阶段\NCommence stage one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,第一阶段！\NStage one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mark！\NMark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,第二阶段！ Mark！\NStage two! Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,温度读数？\NTemperature reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很稳定\NSteady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在预期值范围之内\NWell inside specification.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,上次聚会那晚\NThe night of the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你都可以在上面煎蛋了\Nyou could've fried an egg on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大家还好吗？ - 你没受伤吧？\N- Is everyone okay? - Are you unhurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没事  我们没事\NWe're fine, we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,冷却系统工作很正常\NThe cooling system performed perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,证明设计中的最薄弱的环节\Nillustrating the weakest link in the design.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就是铸造用的金属\NThe metal used for the casing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield\NRenfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我会开始调查所有涉及镍铁合金的\NI'll initiate a survey of all the British steel manufacturers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,英帝国钢铁生产厂\Nthat work with nickel-steel alloys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得螺丝和螺栓\NI don't suppose nuts and bolts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能衡量你的股票\Ncan measure up to your stock in trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？\NSorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  鲜血和肉  当然了\NWhy, flesh and blood, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么比行医更高尚的了\NThere can be no higher calling than the practice of medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,能拯救生命\NThe ability to save lives
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们的努力看起来微不足道\Nmakes all our efforts here seem trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  Grayson先生\NThank you, Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是相似？\NResemblance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不  她就是Ilona\NNo. She is Ilona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子四个世纪以前已经死了\NMy wife died four centuries ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的  我那时在场\NI know. I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她转生\NThen she has been born again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,命运把她带到您身边\Nand the fates have returned her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  你给我听着  Josef\NNow, you listen to me, Josef.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,再也不许提\NYou must never again mention
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina Murray和我妻子有多像了\NMina Murray's resemblance to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听懂了吗？\NDo you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要…对任何人讲\NNever. To anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要去哪里？ - 出去\N- Where are you going? - Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要来杯香槟打发时间？\NPerhaps a glass of champagne to kill the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不  谢谢了\NNo, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,多有趣的小惊喜\NWhat a lovely surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你在花店那里\NI'd expect you to be at the florist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,选牡丹和苹果花呢\Nup to your neck in peonies and apple blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了？  - 没事\N- Is something wrong? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  恩  我在重新考虑\NListen, um, I've been reconsidering the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要在Carfax庄园举办订婚宴\Nof having the engagement party at Carfax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  我觉得不自在\NWell, I-I feel uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,开销很大\NIt's a huge imposition,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  老实说\Nand, well, frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生这样做的动机是什么\NMr. Grayson's motives for hosting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我意思是\NI mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟你只是他的一名员工\Nyou're just one of his employees after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没觉得自己就是个普通员工\NWell, I'd like to think I'm a little more than just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  当然\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是不知道为什么他如此…\NI don't know why he's so interested in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在意我们？\NIn us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他如此乐于关注我们的事\NHe's assumed this very intense involvement
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像…\Nin our relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是其中一员\Nas if he's a part of it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  那是因为\NWell, that's because,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,从某方面来说  他确实是\NI suppose in a way, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们分开的时候\NWhen we split up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是Grayson先生把我拉到一边\Nit was Mr. Grayson who took me aside
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,让我知道自己有多傻\Nand made me realize what a fool I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他让我认识你\NHe made me see you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,并且尊重你本身\Nand respect you for who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不仅仅是一名妻子  母亲\Nnot just a prospective wife and mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也是和我一样\Nbut a woman with aspirations every bit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有追求的女性\Nas important as my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的这样？\NHe did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我本不想告诉你的\NI didn't wanna tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我知道你讨厌这些…\NLook, I know you hate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,繁文缛节\Nall of this bother over arrangements...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:14:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,相当讨厌\NVery much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那就让Lucy打理吧\NSo let Lucy handle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她就以此为生啊\NShe lives for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你所需要做的\NAll you have to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就是准时在宴会出现\Nturn up on time for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那这段时间呢？\NAnd in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,埋头工作\NBury yourself in work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,说的对\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,说的没错\NOf course you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,批完这些卷子后\NOnce you have graded those papers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就去校储藏室\Nyou will find in university
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿有18只待宰羔羊\Nstorage 18 recently slaughtered lambs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,把每只的海马体取出来\NExtract the hippocampus from each
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了\Nand prepare them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,给神经学的学生解剖课用\Nfor dissection by the neurology students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我几个小时后回来\NI shall be back in a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别让我失望\NTry not to disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗？\NIs there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其实  我希望做点儿\NActually, I'd hoped for something
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不这么乏味的事\Na little less prosaic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina  我们必须得打好根基\NNow, now, Mina. We mustn't get ahead of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,宁做勤奋龟  不做偷懒兔  是吧？\NBetter to be the tortoise than the hare, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不做羊就好\NAnything but the lamb, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么巫术？\NWhat is this witchcraft?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是科学\NScience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果成功的话\NIf this works,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就能在阳光下活动\Nthen we shall walk in daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,阳光下行走？\NTo walk in the sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想象吗  主人？\NCan you imagine us, liege?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,无论昼夜\NImmortal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不可战胜  永垂不朽\Ninvincible by night and by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  是的  很激动人心  我确定\NYes, yes, it is all very thrilling, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,（罗马尼亚语）干杯\NNoroc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我能感受到太阳\NI can feel the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我能感觉出温暖\NI can feel its warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,主人\NMaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Josef  不要\NJosef. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  起作用了\NYes, it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这就算成功了？\NYou call this a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你没看到吗？\NDon't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它起作用了\NIt works, but only
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不过就只在注射的组织部位\Nin the tissue surrounding the injection site.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没传运到心脏\NWithout a functioning heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,药剂就没办法散布全身\Nthe serum cannot be distributed throughout your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在需要的\NAll we need now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一剂分散剂\Nis a dispersion agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,问题所在  是生理上的\NThe problem is one of mechanics,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而非化学问题\Nnot chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,心脏就只是一个泵\NThe heart is simply a pump,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其他一无是处\Nnothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能让我心脏运作起来\NIf we can make mine function,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,问题就解决了  对吧？\Nthe problem is solved, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(388,274)}1880年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这些细胞是活的\NThese cells are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢？\NSo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,血细胞离体一小时就会死的\NBlood cells die within an hour or so of extraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这个薄片是1887年的\NThis slide is dated 1887.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是九年前的了\NThat's nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这是你为什么\NAnd this is why you couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不去花店见我的原因？\Nmeet me at the florist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太不可思议了\NThat makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不明白\NWhat I can't understand is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能对你的订婚宴\Nhow you can maintain such a willful
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这么不在乎呢\Ndisinterest in your own engagement party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的Mina  有时和你说话\NHonestly, Mina, it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就像和一个男人一样\Ntalking to a man sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,全心全意的\Nnose buried in whatever silly thing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,埋头苦干那些无聊事儿\Nhas captured his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy  怎么了？\NLucy, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌这样\NI hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy  我…我不明白\NLucy, I-I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会明白的\NYou wouldn't, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你又不是那个一门心思\NYou're not the one attending to every detail
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,打理闺蜜奢华婚宴\Nfor an extravagant party to celebrate the end of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,每个细节的那个人\Nthe only thing that's ever mattered to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lucy  - 真的\N- Lucy.   - It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都不同了\NThings will never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们永远是朋友啊\NWe will always be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  Mina  亲爱的\NOh, Mina, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你那么聪慧  却又如此愚钝\NYou are so terribly clever, yet so terribly stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不  事实是你要结婚了\NNo, you are to be married, and that is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\NYou understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,带上你的东西  咱去喝咖啡\NGet your things. We'll go to the cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太多事要讨论了\NThere's a million things to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  先生\NI am sorry, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人马上就下来\NI am assured my lady will be down presently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那我一直等着\NI have all the time in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生  真意外\NMr. Grayson. How unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须为昨天没去Savoy酒店而道歉\NI must apologize for my absence from dinner at the Savoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然事不可免\NIt was as inexcusable
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不可原谅\Nas it was unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  拜托  我都忘了\NOh, please, I had forgotten about it entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,希望今晚可以有幸相伴\NI was hoping I might make amends by
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,以作补偿\Nrequesting the pleasure of your company this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么\NIf there is one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,让我特烦你们美国人的话\NI find tiresome about you Americans,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你们不懈的乐观精神了\Nit is your relentless optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证你以后\NI promise you a spectacle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,会难忘今宵的\Nthat you will not soon forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  Grayson先生\NCome now, Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想当然  像你这种富人\NSurely, a man of your affluence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很随意就能找一个晚餐伴侣\Ncan find a dinner companion for the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\NCertainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只是这特别的娱乐项目\NIt's just that this particular diversion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,普通女人可承受不了\Nis beyond the petty refinements of other women.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你有能力全然欣赏\NOnly you possess the sensibilities to appreciate it fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你这奉承也太明显了\NYour flattery is too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,奉承这种笨方法\NFlattery is a dull blade that I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是绝不会对你用的\Nwould never employ against one such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这活动  如果不能让我满意\NThis diversion, if it displeases me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:22:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你就别再找我了\Nyou will agree not to call on me ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好  - 真的？\N- Yes. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.25,0:24:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Elsa  厨佣\NElsa, from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.59,0:24:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天啊\NOh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.05,0:24:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想她没有近亲吧\NI trust she has no close relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.52,0:24:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,和所有员工一样\NLike all our staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.04,0:24:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会发现她不在了\Nnone close enough to note her absence,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我会想念她做的苹果蛋糕\Nthough I will miss her apple crumb cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.87,0:24:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的Cervenka\NBloody Cervenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经询问了Shaw将军麾下三人\NI've interviewed three men from Shaw's regiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.20,0:25:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,两个政敌\Ntwo political opponents and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.41,0:25:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一个被开了的军助\Nan adjunct who was dishonorably discharged,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.35,0:25:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没人说一句坏话\Nand none had a bad word to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.30,0:25:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像很失望\NYou sound disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.97,0:25:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我没失望\NNo, I'm not disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.40,0:25:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不明白\NIt's just I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.28,0:25:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么Grayson对此感兴趣\Nwhy Grayson's so interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.83,0:25:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  坦白讲\NI mean, frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.97,0:25:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我从小就很仰慕Shaw将军\NI've admired Shaw since I was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.71,0:25:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,上学的时候\NI actually chose him
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.81,0:25:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我还拿他当传记研究对象\Nfor a subject for a biography in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.31,0:25:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道一些相当奇怪的事吗？\NDo you wanna know something very, very odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.85,0:25:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.83,0:25:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,从我最近做的调查来看\NFor all my recent digging,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.69,0:25:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只说明一件事儿\NI've not been able to uncover one single fact
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.82,0:25:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就是并没什么发现\Nthat I didn't include back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.34,0:25:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也许本就没什么可说的\NPerhaps there is nothing more to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.74,0:25:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N- That's why. - Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.13,0:25:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我  Szabo\NTell me something, Szabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.20,0:25:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过没有任何秘密的人吗？\NHave you ever met a man without any secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.77,0:25:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,上周我自己\NI've destroyed over half
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.97,0:25:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就杀了不止六个吸血鬼\Na dozen Nosferatu in the last week alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.04,0:25:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是被主人召唤的\Nand they are summoned by their sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.18,0:25:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我知道你对那个美国人的顾虑\NNow, I-I share your concerns about the American,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.50,0:26:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但他现在不是我们面对的最大威胁\Nbut he is hardly the greatest threat that we face.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.26,0:26:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,同意  但我们也别低估了Grayson\NAgreed, but we must not underestimate Grayson
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.50,0:26:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还有他的财力\Nnor the power of his purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.14,0:26:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管Harker和他\NMaking inroads with his man Harker
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个开始\Nis a start, but nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.64,0:26:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我认为Grayson值得查下\NYes, I think Grayson does bear scrutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.97,0:26:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jayne说的对\NI agree with Jayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.43,0:26:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就不劳组织动手了\NThe Order needn't be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.71,0:26:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我会派人盯着的\NI shall see to it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.69,0:26:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  有消息通知我\NGood. Keep me informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.33,0:26:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我们的贵客来了\NAh, our distinguished guests have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.78,0:26:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎啊  Shaw将军  Ogilvy将军\NWelcome, General Shaw, General Ogilvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.59,0:26:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人  大人\NMy lady. My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.90,0:26:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有请  先生们  请坐\NPlease, gentlemen, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.13,0:26:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  将军\NSo, general,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.70,0:26:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,您保证过在三月份\Nyou assured us total control of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.26,0:26:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就能完全掌控波斯油田\Nthe Persian oil fields by March.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.56,0:26:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对  没错  但你也知道\NYes, of course, but as you may know,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.08,0:26:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,情况变得略微复杂了\Nthe situation has become much more complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.10,0:26:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,何以见得？  愿闻其详\NHow so? Please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能？ - 当然\N- May I? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.57,0:26:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,自从苏丹颁布了法令\NOur provocateurs have been
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.37,0:26:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,规定退斩无赦\Nunable to foment so much as a border skirmish
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.70,0:27:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的卧底就不能\Nsince the sultan issued a decree
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.00,0:27:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,随意煽动边境冲突了\Nto his men to stand down under pain of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.64,0:27:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你也瞧见了\NSo you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.58,0:27:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,发动先发制人的全面入侵\Nthere's little we can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.74,0:27:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无能为力\Nsave a full-scale preemptive invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.04,0:27:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  议会也绝不会…\NOf course, parliament would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.05,0:27:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,深表遗憾  Show将军\NMy condolences, General Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.20,0:27:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\NI'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.33,0:27:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogilvy将军上吊自杀了\NIt appears General Ogilvy hanged himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.80,0:27:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他的属下明天早晨\NHis adjunct will discover him
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.11,0:27:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,会在他房间的浴室发现他的尸体\Nin the washroom of his quarters tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.01,0:27:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真悲哀\NTragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.05,0:27:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么将军  我们什么时候\NSo, general, when can we expect
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.97,0:28:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,能开始进攻奥斯曼帝国?\Nto begin the Ottoman offensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.69,0:28:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,八月怎么样?\NShall we say August?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.26,0:28:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.53,0:28:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就八月\NAugust.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.09,0:28:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这案子很有趣\NIt is an interesting case,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.36,0:28:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,需要发挥你的特殊才能\None which requires your particular talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.83,0:28:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你的目的是什么?\NWhat are your intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.14,0:28:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,找到Alexander Grayson在这世上的\NDiscover the one thing Mr. Alexander Grayson
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.54,0:28:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一件挚爱之物\Nloves most in all the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.14,0:28:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.24,0:28:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,腐化它  毁坏它\NCorrupt it. Deface it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.91,0:28:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,将它从世上抹去\NObliterate it from this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.08,0:28:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,组织知道你的计划吗?\NIs the Order aware of your intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.05,0:28:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道我在调查Grayson先生\NThey're aware that I'm investigating Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.09,0:28:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,请回答我的问题\NPlease. Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.25,0:28:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我一样清楚他们会怎样\NWell, you know as well as I that if they did,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.29,0:28:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我会被逼解释我的动机\NI would be forced to explain my motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.38,0:28:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说\NYou mean your son's recent suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.29,0:28:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子殉情自杀?\Nafter the death of his lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.66,0:28:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  Kleiberson女士\NPlease, Miss Kleiberson.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.70,0:28:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想澄清事实\NI only wish to clarify the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.17,0:28:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是…\Nand that is thus...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.33,0:28:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你想利用我\NYou wish to employ my services
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.77,0:29:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,来执行未经批准的行动\Nin order to execute an unsanctioned operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.68,0:29:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过  并非完全未经批准\NAs I said before, not completely unsanctioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.25,0:29:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.75,0:29:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那这件事上\NMay I then rely on your
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.54,0:29:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我可否完全信赖您会保守秘密\Ncomplete discretion in this matter
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.91,0:29:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好让我另寻合伙人呢?\Nso that I may engage another contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.52,0:29:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不必要\NThat will not be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.56,0:29:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定接手这个案子\NI have decided to accept the assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.16,0:29:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就算未经批准?\NDespite it being unsanctioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.26,0:29:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为没经批准\NBecause it is unsanctioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.76,0:29:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要求双倍酬劳\NI will require double my standard fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.84,0:29:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  包括支出\NPlus expenses, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.91,0:29:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.25,0:29:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker先生吗?\NMr. Harker?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.30,0:30:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(271,362)\fn华文行楷\fs22\c&H02F8F6&}欲知Show真相  四轮马车接头\N 今晚九点  前来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.98,0:30:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎贵夫人今晚想见我\NIt seems Her Ladyship wishes to see me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.32,0:30:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,详情未知\NNo details.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.78,0:30:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真有趣\NHow intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.22,0:30:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  Cervenka先生还要在这儿呆多久?\NSir, how long is Mr. Cervenka going to be our guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.19,0:30:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了\NYou heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.36,0:30:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,随便他\NAs long as he wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.30,0:30:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你有意见?\NDo you have any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.17,0:30:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NOh, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.30,0:30:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很多意见…\Nquite a growing number of objections...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.64,0:30:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,最主要的是他缺乏谨慎\NChief among which is his lack of discretion
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.14,0:30:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没自制力\Nand complete absence of self-control.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.01,0:30:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.21,0:30:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他很冲动\NHe can be impetuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.45,0:30:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但Josef在战场上\NBut Josef has saved my life on the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.29,0:30:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,救过我无数次\Nmore times than I care to count.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.79,0:30:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他与我情同兄弟\NHe's like my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.39,0:31:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,胜似兄弟\Nmore than my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.62,0:31:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他的忠诚毋庸置疑\NHis loyalty is absolute,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.99,0:31:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也对我绝对服从\Nand he will obey my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.60,0:31:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此\NNevertheless, he has demonstrated
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.56,0:31:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他的服从和忠诚\Nthat his obedience and loyalty fall
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.90,0:31:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,与他的本性相去甚远\Na distant second and third to his nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.84,0:31:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能被驯服\NHe cannot be domesticated,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.09,0:31:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不能完全信任\Nnor fully trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.81,0:31:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.81,0:31:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,其一  他知道你对Murray女士的情意\NHe knows your true feelings toward Miss Murray, for one,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.31,0:31:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,且知道其中渊源\Nand their origins.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.05,0:31:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经让他发誓保守秘密\NI've sworn his silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.12,0:31:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信他会保守秘密\NA silence I'm sure he means to keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.22,0:31:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只是不知道他能保守多久\Nbut only insofar as he's capable of keeping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.79,0:31:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我担忧的不是他的忠诚\NIt's not his loyalty that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.49,0:31:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真高兴你能来\NI'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.16,0:31:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这些最好亲自处理\NThese things are best done in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.63,0:31:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\NWhat things?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.66,0:31:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,351)}我对昨晚的宴会很开心\NWell, I did enjoy our soiree last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.73,0:32:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(365,347)}你的陪伴\Nand I do find your company,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.06,0:32:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,345)}也让人十分愉悦\Non occasion, most agreeable,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.40,0:32:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,346)}但我必须结束这段关系\Nbut I'm afraid I must terminate this relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.37,0:32:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,早预料到了这悲惨的一幕\NHow distressingly predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.27,0:32:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说什么?  - 没什么\N- Excuse me? - Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.71,0:32:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我先走了  - 不  等等\N- I'll be on my way. - No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.15,0:32:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好奇\NI'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.15,0:32:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得预料的这一幕\NExactly what is this predictability
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.45,0:32:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如此...   - 悲伤吗?\N- that you find so... - Distressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.15,0:32:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,比起悲伤  更觉得是失望\NWell, not so much distressing as disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.32,0:32:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.55,0:32:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,情况很清楚\NThe situation is clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.41,0:32:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  显而易见\Ncrystal clear, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.83,0:32:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 要我继续说下去?  - 请讲\N- Must I go on? - Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.76,0:32:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一个以驯服男人\NYou're a woman who takes great pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.23,0:32:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为乐的女人\Nin asserting her domination over men.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.57,0:32:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然而  一旦驯服\NHowever, once you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.70,0:32:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你就对他们失去兴趣\Nyou very soon grow bored with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.67,0:32:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,讲得很对  继续\NTrue enough. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.54,0:32:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,自我们相遇\NSince we met, you've made every effort
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.54,0:32:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你就想方设法驯服我\Nto do the same with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.14,0:32:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,然而你却彻底失败了\Nand in this, you have utterly failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.04,0:32:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.08,0:32:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,未能成功驯服我\NThis failure to dominate me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.55,0:32:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,使你对我感到迷恋\Nhas led to you being infatuated with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.72,0:32:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而这强烈的情感\NSuch is the intensity of your emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.85,0:32:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,威胁到了你的独立与控制欲\Nthat they threaten your sense of independence and control.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.39,0:32:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,而再次掌握控制的唯一途径\NThe only way to reassert this control
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.62,0:33:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就是结束我们的关系\Nis by terminating our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.16,0:33:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你太自恋了\NOh, you do flatter yourself so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.36,0:33:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要结束关系\NYour vulnerability is evident
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.11,0:33:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就暴露了你的脆弱\Nby your withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.13,0:33:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做真的很怯懦\NI call your actions cowardice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.77,0:33:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧你这无聊的论调\NI call your ploys tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.50,0:33:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你依然认为你对我毫无感觉?\NYou still assert that you feel nothing for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.97,0:33:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有\NNothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.81,0:33:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  跟我来\NFollow me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.35,0:33:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生  这边  - 今晚的约会对象?\N- This way, sir. - Tonight's engagement?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.98,0:33:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NI imagine so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.05,0:33:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他来的时候看到我也在\NAnd does it give you great pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.55,0:33:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是很高兴?\Nto see me here as he arrives?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.25,0:33:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生  游戏…\NThe game, Mr. Grayson,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.95,0:33:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,都需要至少三个玩家\Nrequires at least three players.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.16,0:33:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天  夫人\NSomeday, madam,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.83,0:33:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你会发现我不是玩玩而已\Nyou'll realize I was never playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.44,0:33:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,女猎人玩弄了你\NThe huntress made a fool of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.37,0:33:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道什么\NYou know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.58,0:33:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟踪了你\NI followed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.28,0:33:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,每个字听得真真切切\NI heard every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.11,0:33:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谁允许你跟踪我的?\NWho gave you permission to follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.92,0:34:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚你回来的时候\NI could smell her stink on you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.78,0:34:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我就闻到了她的臭味\Nwhen you returned home last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.02,0:34:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信\NI could never have believed you would consort
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.89,0:34:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟和这样可鄙的生物交往\Nwith such a despicable creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.50,0:34:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白吗?\NDo you not understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.87,0:34:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的策略非常复杂\NWe have a very complex strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.17,0:34:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,其中会有些让人不爽\NSome of our tactics are distasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.67,0:34:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是恶心  - 也许吧\N- Disgusting. - Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.97,0:34:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果想胜利\NBut they are necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.41,0:34:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就必须这样做\Nif we are to emerge victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.88,0:34:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在玩一场危险\NWe are playing a very dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.57,0:34:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而不可饶恕的游戏\Nand a very unforgiving game.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.28,0:34:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,引诱他们的女猎人\NBy seducing their huntress,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.62,0:34:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,把她从游戏中剔除\NI take her out of their game.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.72,0:34:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样行不通了\NAh, but not anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.79,0:34:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她\Nbecause there she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.39,0:34:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,回到游戏中了\Nback on the board,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.46,0:34:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,追捕我们  杀害我们\Nhunting us, killing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.53,0:34:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得我们是猎人\NDo you not remember when we were the hunters
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.37,0:34:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是猎物的时候了吗?\Nand they were the prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.17,0:34:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是怎样在早餐前\NWhy, you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.44,0:34:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就捕获上百的猎物\Nwould harvest a hundred souls before breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.41,0:35:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我的君主啊\NPlease, my liege.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.95,0:35:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我恳求您  让我杀了她\NI beseech thee. Let me kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.13,0:35:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让她惨叫\NMake her scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.21,0:35:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker先生?\NMr. Harker?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.32,0:35:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你把便条给我的?\NYou sent me the note?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.62,0:35:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫Peter Lang\NPeter Lang,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,曾是女王陛下步枪旅下士\Nformally Corporal Lang of Her Majesty's rifle brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.10,0:36:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道Shaw的底细?\NYou have the truth I seek regarding Shaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.77,0:36:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  给我十块才告诉你\NI do. Cost you 10 bob to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.05,0:36:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我这有个地址\NI've got an address for you and a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.42,0:36:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,以及Vera Markham这名字\Na lady called Vera Markham.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.09,0:36:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她和他什么关系?\NWho is she to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.23,0:36:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己去查吧\NSee for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.95,0:36:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁?\NWho is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.92,0:37:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Jonathan Harker\NUh, my name's Jonathan Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.69,0:37:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事?\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.83,0:37:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我找Vera Markham\NI'm looking for Vera Markham.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.93,0:37:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是\NI'm Vera Markham.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.90,0:38:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.90,0:38:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  天啊  噢  我的天哪\NOh, God. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.03,0:38:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你死了\NI thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.70,0:38:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的心...  - 刚有个男人\N- Your heart... - There was a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.50,0:38:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  他走了\NNo, no, he's gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.33,0:38:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他走了  已经走了\Nhe's gone, he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.04,0:38:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他走了  你把他吓走了\NHe's gone. You scared him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.24,0:38:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  天哪  噢  你救了我\NOh, God. Oh, you saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.55,0:38:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚在我卧室干什么?\NWhat were you doing in my bedroom in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.29,0:38:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时失眠\NI suffer from insomnia from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.36,0:38:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,习惯夜里散步\Nand it's my habit to take long, nighttime walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.16,0:38:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(367,357)}近来  发现自己很喜欢\NAs of late, I find myself
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.26,0:38:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(375,361)}在这条街上走\Nincreasingly drawn to this street.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.46,0:39:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们要找的人?\NThe one we've been searching for?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.63,0:39:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是的\NI believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.80,0:39:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以伦敦再次解放了?\NSo London is free again?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.27,0:39:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好\NExcellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.48,0:39:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  先生\NThank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.28,0:39:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管是用的你的方法\NYour methods, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.08,0:39:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的方法太鲁莽蛮干了\NIt was reckless, foolhardy, even,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.01,0:39:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至把它引诱到你家里\Nto lure such a creature into your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.78,0:39:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 会不会有可能他...   - 不会的\N- There was every chance he... - There was no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.12,0:39:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但你得...  - 没机会\N- But surely you must see... - There was no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.70,0:40:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会认出她的\NYou would not have recognized her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.37,0:40:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,潜心悔过\NSo contrite,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.24,0:40:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,温柔可人\Nso gentle,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.20,0:40:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,腼腆羞涩\Nso shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.38,0:40:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我驯服她了\NI have sheared the tiger's claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.41,0:40:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,正如您所说  先生\NJust as you said you would, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.95,0:40:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管有人怀疑过我\NAlthough some doubted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.65,0:40:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她再也看不见我了\NShe'll never see me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.65,0:40:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会已经失去最强的武器\NThe Ordo Draco has lost its most dangerous weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.16,0:40:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,却还不知情\Nand it doesn't even know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.89,0:40:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而你也一道儿处理了Josef\NAnd you were able to remove Josef in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.33,0:40:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,妙哉\NA masterstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.06,0:40:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.97,0:40:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起  先生  - 没关系\N- I'm sorry, sir. - Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.24,0:40:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Josef是一名士兵\NJosef was a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.34,0:40:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他会明白的\NHe would have understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.78,0:41:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有时  你必须牺牲骑士\NSometimes, you have to sacrifice a knight
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.45,0:41:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,才能俘获女王\Nto capture a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.36,0:41:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Josef  再见\NGood-bye, Josef.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.94,0:41:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,明天  Renfield  我们回去工作\NTomorrow, we get back to work, Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.74,0:41:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要共鸣器的合金\NWe need that alloy for the resonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.34,0:41:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.46,0:41:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人  我来帮您\NMa'am, may I help you with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.83,0:41:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…\NWha...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.17,0:42:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是警察  他是罪犯\NPolice business. He's a known criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.28,0:42:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不必恐慌\NNo cause for alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.00,0:42:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快点儿  快离开这儿\NCome on, let's get out of here.
